high_descs: Walk forward to the white table by the stove
Pick up the green apple from the table
Turn around and walk over to the microwave in the corner
Heat the apple in the microwave then remove it
Turn around and walk forward and right to the small black table
Put the apple on the small table
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple on the small dark table

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table in front of you.
Grab a yellow apple from the table.
Go to the microwave behind you and to the right.
Put the apple in the microwave, then grab it.
Walk to the end table to the left of the sink.
Place the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Warm an apple and put it on a table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the white table.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk until you're near the table the microwave is on then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and take two steps then turn left and walk to the white table then turn right and walk to the black table.
Put the apple near the front right corner of the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the table.
